com.viaoa.sync.remote

Interface RemoteClientInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RemoteClientImpl

    @OARemoteInterface
public interface RemoteClientInterface
    Client remote methods that will use the same named msg queue as RemoteSync, when set up (bind) on the server. This is so that changes can be ordered and instances (clients/server0 will stay in sync.
    Author:
    vvia
